<li>University folklore and anthropology departments that host oral-history collections.</li>
<li>National and city-specific archival collections: The National Archives (UK), Archives de Paris, National Archives of Singapore, Archivo General de la Nación (Mexico), National Library of Argentina.</li>
</ul>
